<item>
            <title>[SEC-1388] Support for custom AuthenticationDetailsSource in form-login tag.</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SEC-1388</link>
                <project id="10040" key="SEC">Spring Security</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When using the &amp;lt;form-login /&amp;gt; tag, there&#180;s no way to configure a custom AuthenticationDetailsSource.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The workaround is to reconfigure UsernamePasswordAuthenticationFilter as a custom filter and reconfigure LoginUrlAuthenticationEntryPoint with its loginFormUrl property. Spring XML becomes more polluted and some minor functionality like the &amp;lt;http&amp;gt; auto-config and the built-in form login page are lost.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
